name: THE SECOND HORSEMAN: SIGIL OF WAR
description:
"When He broke the second seal, I heard the second living creature saying, "Come." 
And another, a red horse, went out; and to him who sat on it, 
it was granted to take peace from Earth, and that men would slay one another; 
and a great sword was given to him."
— Revelation 6:3–4

800x800gif made on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
